response.explain: The execution error indicates that the oven is already on (togglable state is not 0) and the lasagna is not yet cookable (cookable state is not 1). This suggests that the lasagna is not properly placed inside the oven, which is why it cannot be cooked.
response.subtask:
(1) Open the oven
(2) Grasp the lasagna
(3) Put the lasagna inside the oven
(4) Turn on the oven
(5) Wait for the lasagna to be cooked
